org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Annexes.VSL.DataTypes

Interface BoundedSubtype

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoundedSubtypeImpl

    public interface BoundedSubtype
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Bounded Subtype'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Type
    • Min Value
    • Max Value
    • Is Min Open
    • Is Max Open
    • Base Data Type
    See Also:
    DataTypesPackage.getBoundedSubtype()
